(44, 'Retail', 'Panasonic for Retail', 'retails', NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Meeting the twin challenges of rapidly changing buyer behaviours and digital disruption. We<br>at Panasonic are experts at adapting to change. We&rsquo;ll work closely with you, to help you keep<br>ahead of your competitors. From electronic shelf labels to interactive displays, intelligent<br>analytics to versatile Ink-base products, we can help you develop solutions that make the<br>customer experience unforgettable, not just in the future, but today.</p>', '17128384146617d70e1417a.svg', '17128421386617e59ac5ca3.svg', '[{\"bsectionid\":1,\"btitle\":\"Connected solutions for Retail\",\"bcontent\":\"When the future of retail depends on successful new ways to engage customers, we provide the solutions you need to create unique and immersive in-store experiences.\",\"bimage\":\"171272865166162a4bbdc36.jpg\"}]', 1, '2024-04-10 05:46:40', '2024-06-21 11:13:44'),
(45, 'Corporate', 'Panasonic for Corporate', 'corporate', NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Enhancing attendee engagement and fostering productive environments is achievable for<br>companies through the adoption of a comprehensive suite of AV solutions. These<br>technologies cater to specific needs and requirements, crafting dynamic meeting spaces<br>tailored to scale. From interactive touch screen displays to high-definition projectors and<br>advanced meeting room management solutions, Panasonic offers a single-source solution to<br>fulfill all your requirements.</p>', '1712731632661635f0c06df.png', '17128414716617e2ff22ccf.png', '[{\"bsectionid\":1,\"btitle\":\"Moving the world forward\",\"bcontent\":\"Take meetings to the next level. Share ideas on multi-touch interactive displays.\\u00a0Or just deliver more engagement for customers, visitors or guests we have the solutions you\\r\\nneed.\",\"bimage\":\"171272866866162a5c188a2.jpg\"}]', 1, '2024-04-10 05:46:52', '2024-06-18 06:25:31'),
(46, 'Education', 'Embracing a connected, engaged and interactive campus.', 'education', NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Students today have grown up in a connected world. How they think about<br>technology and education, and how they interact inside and outside of the classroom, has<br>changed dramatically. Schools, eager to be at the forefront of innovation, need to adapt to<br>these new expectations and capitalize on new opportunities. With industry-leading display<br>and audio solutions, we&rsquo;re enabling the kind of dynamic connectivity that will keep students<br>engaged, simplify how instructors educate and maintain campus safety.</p>', '17127314496616353909a98.svg', '17128395156617db5b86f17.svg', '[{\"bsectionid\":1,\"btitle\":\"Technology to Enable Active Learning\",\"bcontent\":\"A collaborative classroom is an ideal active learning environment. We support to\\u00a0improve the quality of active learning experiences with our products and technology.\",\"bimage\":\"171272868766162a6fc849e.jpg\"}]', 1, '2024-04-10 05:47:04', '2024-06-18 06:26:21'),
(47, 'Transport Hub', 'Panasonic for Transport Hubs', 'transport-hub', NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>In the realm of professional displays, the networking capabilities and digital signage<br>functionality enables brands to stand out from the pack at any prominent transport hubs like<br>railway stations, airports, metro stations etc.Our Displays and LED offers an unparalleled<br>level of brightness, producing vivid colours that stand out even in brightly lit transport hubs.<br>When displays are being used as an additional advertising revenue source, it&rsquo;s important that<br>they draw the eye, so Panasonic&rsquo;s technology really helps to make content stand out.</p>', '1712731613661635dd50980.png', '17128416916617e3db7a7e1.png', '[{\"bsectionid\":1,\"btitle\":\"Moving the world forward\",\"bcontent\":\"Count on Panasonic to provide the latest advancements in innovative solutions\\u00a0especially important in the medical field for critical applications.\",\"bimage\":\"171272870366162a7f766cb.jpg\"}]', 1, '2024-04-10 05:47:18', '2024-06-18 06:27:11'),
(48, 'Restaurant', 'Panasonic for Restaurants', 'restaurant', NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Panasonic\'s technology can enhance profitability by seamlessly connecting every aspect of your<br>restaurant, empowering customers with real-time data for smarter, more efficient operations. Our<br>vibrant and versatile displays elevate the ambiance of any restaurant, enabling better service<br>delivery and enhancing customer engagement.</p>', '17127314666616354a2dd70.svg', '17128422706617e61e38df3.svg', '[{\"bsectionid\":1,\"btitle\":\"One Seamless Customer Experience\",\"bcontent\":\"Count on Panasonic to provide the latest advancements in innovative solutions\\u00a0especially important in the medical field for critical applications.\",\"bimage\":\"171272872666162a96ccc4f.jpg\"}]', 1, '2024-04-10 05:47:29', '2024-06-18 06:33:27'),
(49, 'Entertainment', 'Panasonic for Entertainment', 'entertainment', NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>As the channels of communication multiply, as the eSports universe expands, drawing<br>millions of followers, the media and entertainment industry is an exciting place to be. But the<br>equipment and software you need to stay ahead keeps evolving. That&rsquo;s why you need a<br>partner capable of maintaining the balance between constantly innovating, and future-<br>proofing the equipment &ndash; and building it robustly enough to last for years to come.</p>', '1712731580661635bc431f1.png', '17128417526617e4188fa18.png', '[{\"bsectionid\":1,\"btitle\":\"Un-limit your audience\\u2019s expectations\",\"bcontent\":\"As media moves beyond simply informing and entertaining, towards immersive,\\u00a0in-person experiences, partner with the experts helping to define its course.\",\"bimage\":\"171272874566162aa9294a6.jpg\"}]', 1, '2024-04-10 05:47:40', '2024-06-18 06:34:10'),
(50, 'Healthcare', 'Panasonic for Healthcare', 'healthcare', NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>We are in a new era of healthcare. It&rsquo;s about leveraging technology that simultaneously<br>increases staff productivity and improves patient experience. The new healthcare brings more<br>people into a conversation even if they can&rsquo;t be in the same room, so information can flow<br>freely across an organization through tightly integrated networks. Learn how we&rsquo;re making<br>the new healthcare possible with our versatile audio-video technology, sophisticated<br>monitoring systems, rugged mobile devices, and healthy indoor air quality solutions.</p>', '171281895566178b0b3e24d.png', '17128396026617dbb223a86.png', '[{\"bsectionid\":1,\"btitle\":\"Where Technology Meets Humanity\",\"bcontent\":\"Count on Panasonic to provide the latest advancements in innovative solutions\\u00a0especially important in the medical field for critical applications.\",\"bimage\":\"171272876166162ab9a932a.jpg\"}]', 1, '2024-04-10 05:47:50', '2024-06-18 06:34:54'),
(51, 'Public Sector', 'Panasonic for Public Sector', 'public-sector', NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Our professional displays and solutions are dedicated to empowering education, enhancing<br>security, optimizing transportation, and supporting government initiatives to foster societal<br>advancement. With cutting-edge technology and tailored solutions, we strive to elevate every<br>aspect of society for a brighter future. Trust us to deliver excellence in every project, driving<br>positive change and progress.</p>', '171281894366178affce090.png', '17128396226617dbc6d3755.png', '[{\"bsectionid\":1,\"btitle\":\"Connecting and improving society\",\"bcontent\":\"When you work in the public sector, the technology you employ often has to\\u00a0work 24\\/7 \\u2013 with 100% uptime the minimum requirement.to support you.\",\"bimage\":\"171272878266162ace3394b.jpg\"}]', 1, '2024-04-10 05:48:29', '2024-06-18 06:35:32');
