(455, 45, 'Banner 25 (410x220) - Display.jpg', 'High visibility Display', 'With high-brightness and high haze value panels to suppress the reflected glare of bright\r\nlight, Panasonic displays are ideal for conference rooms, meeting rooms and open spaces\r\nsuch as receptions.', 1, 0, 'Right', '2024-06-18 06:25:31', '2024-06-18 06:25:31'),
(456, 45, 'Banner 26 (410x220) - Touch Display.jpg', 'Interactive Touch Display', 'Enables writing on the display screen and equipped with a whiteboard function. By setting\r\nthe USB receiver of the mouse on the display, you can use the mouse to write on the display\r\nscreen and zoom in/out. This is useful for facilitating efficient meetings.', 1, 0, 'Left', '2024-06-18 06:25:31', '2024-06-18 06:25:31'),
(457, 45, 'Banner 27 (410x220) - E-Sign Cards.jpg', 'eSignCard', 'Businesses can utilize\r\neSignCards to display schedules,\r\nspeaker profiles, and sponsor\r\ninformation during conferences.\r\nTheir clean, purposeful, and\r\nminimalist design make them\r\nideal for placement in\r\nBoardrooms, Conference Halls,\r\nand Top Management Cabins.', 1, 0, 'Right', '2024-06-18 06:25:31', '2024-06-18 06:25:31'),
(458, 45, 'RB_PoE_wall_mount-booked-press (1).png', 'RoomBook+', 'RoomBook+ is the simplest\r\nsolution for managing meeting\r\nrooms, optimizing board room\r\nuse, and displaying relevant\r\ninformation where it is needed\r\nthe most. Built on years of\r\ncustomer feedback, RoomBook+\r\nis designed to upgrade the\r\nmeeting culture and introduce\r\nmeeting space room\r\nmanagement to the modern\r\nworkplace.', 1, 0, 'Left', '2024-06-18 06:25:31', '2024-06-18 06:25:31'),
(459, 45, 'electronicshelflabels-benefitsforyourcustomers.jpg', 'Electronic Shelf Labels', 'Gone are the days of static, paper-based\r\nbadges; electronic name tags offer\r\ndynamic capabilities that not only display\r\na person\'s name and title but also\r\nintegrate seamlessly with organizational\r\nsystems. These futuristic devices allow\r\nfor real-time updates, enabling instant\r\nchanges to be made to titles, affiliations,\r\nand other pertinent information.\r\nMoreover, electronic name tags can\r\nfacilitate smoother networking\r\nexperiences, providing quick access to\r\ncontact details as well as smooth\r\ntransition of seats in case of migration.', 1, 0, 'Right', '2024-06-18 06:25:31', '2024-06-18 06:25:31'),
(460, 45, 'Banner 30 (410x220) - Pro-meet.jpg', 'Pro-meet', 'Pro-meet wireless collaboration\r\nsolutions allows meeting rooms to be\r\nde-cluttered by getting rid of cables.\r\nWith Pro-meet, users can share up to 4\r\nscreens simultaneously allowing\r\nseamless interaction and collaboration.\r\nAirplay and Miracast support means no\r\nneed for additional applications.', 1, 0, 'Left', '2024-06-18 06:25:31', '2024-06-18 06:25:31'),
(461, 46, 'Banner 28 (410x220) - Touch Display.jpg', 'Interactive Displays', '85% of us are visual learners. With their unrivalled brightness, clarity, and up to 10 touch\r\npoints, our multi-touch displays get the message across, interactively.', 1, 0, 'Left', '2024-06-18 06:26:21', '2024-06-18 06:26:21'),
(462, 46, 'Banner 29 (410x220) - Projector.jpg', 'Projectors', 'Powerful daylight projectors. Maintenance-free laser projectors. Short throw projectors for\r\nsmall classrooms. Just some of the ways we help you project sharper, brighter, further – and\r\nfor longer.', 1, 0, 'Right', '2024-06-18 06:26:21', '2024-06-18 06:26:21'),
(463, 46, 'Banner 30 (410x220) - Pro-meet.jpg', 'Pro-meet', 'Pro-meet wireless collaboration features allow students as well as teachers to interact, share\r\nand present their ideas seamlessly. Capable of sharing up to 4 screens, this allows teachers to\r\nperform comparative analysis and enable interactive education. Moderator and DnD features\r\nwill allow for a seamless teaching experience.', 1, 0, 'Left', '2024-06-18 06:26:22', '2024-06-18 06:26:22'),
(464, 46, 'Banner 31 (410x220) - Roombook+.jpg', 'RoomBook+', 'RoomBook+ is the simplest solution for monitoring classroom utilization and displaying\r\nrelevant information where it is needed the most. Built on years of customer feedback,\r\nRoomBook+ is designed to upgrade and introduce digital classroom schedule management to\r\nthe modern-day institutions.', 1, 0, 'Right', '2024-06-18 06:26:22', '2024-06-18 06:26:22'),
(465, 47, 'Banner 33 (410x220) - Signage, Panasonic for Transport Hub.jpg', 'Long Life 24/7 Panel with Tough Glass', 'Easily present advertising, interactive information and focused content utilising the 24/7 long\r\nlife panels via landscape or portrait orientation. Ideal for rail transit and other industries.', 1, 0, 'Left', '2024-06-18 06:27:11', '2024-06-18 06:27:11'),
(466, 47, 'sf2h_instimg_01_high.jpg', 'Floor Stand Kiosk', 'There are a range of floor standing digital standees available in both standard and Slim\r\ndesign. Standard design offers both touch and non-touch screen options. Advertising display,\r\ninteractive information release and other functions in indoor environments.', 1, 0, 'Right', '2024-06-18 06:27:11', '2024-06-18 06:27:11'),
(467, 47, 'Banner 32 (410x220) - LED Screen,Panasonic for Transport Hub.jpg', 'LED Video Wall', 'LED Video wall series which you can add panels to, creating a giant, immersive experience.\r\nSuitable for security monitoring and airports and much more.', 1, 0, 'Left', '2024-06-18 06:27:12', '2024-06-18 06:27:12'),
(468, 47, 'public24h_high.jpg', 'Transport SignEdge', 'Intelligent information display software for flights, buses, and railways. An advance\r\nPassenger Information Display System (PIDS) shows real time information flights, rains to\r\nthe passengers at airports, bus, trains and at others.', 1, 0, 'Right', '2024-06-18 06:27:12', '2024-06-18 06:27:12'),
(469, 48, 'Banner 34 (410x220) - Display, Panasonic for Restaurant.jpg', 'High Brightness Displays', 'Present promotional offers, menus and other information content utilising the high brightness,\r\n4K, 24/7 long life panels via landscape or portrait orientation. Ideal for high lit ambient\r\nenvironment of restaurants and QSR.', 1, 0, 'Left', '2024-06-18 06:33:27', '2024-06-18 06:33:27'),
(470, 48, 'Banner 35 (410x220) -  Signage, Panasonic for Restaurant.jpg', 'QSR SignEdge', 'Showcase dynamic digital menus seamlessly integrated with your current point-of-sale\r\nsystem. Your digital menu boards will automatically update in real-time whenever you make\r\nchanges to pricing, inventory availability, or any other menu details linked to your POS.', 1, 0, 'Right', '2024-06-18 06:33:27', '2024-06-18 06:33:27'),
(471, 48, 'Screenshot 2024-06-13 182049.png', 'eSignCard', 'Restaurants and cafes can enhance the dining experience by replacing traditional paper tent cards with interactive digital\r\nversions, featuring vivid images and detailed descriptions. eSignCards can be strategically placed to highlight ongoing\r\npromotions, menus, or new product introductions Their clean, purposeful, and minimalist design make them ideal for\r\nrestaurants', 1, 0, 'Left', '2024-06-18 06:33:27', '2024-06-18 06:33:27'),
(472, 49, '1716202139664b2a9b7c1cc.jpg', 'Broadcast & ProAV', 'From live camera systems to remote camera set-ups. From a single robotic camera to an\r\nentire IT/IP Video Process Platform.', 1, 0, 'Left', '2024-06-18 06:34:10', '2024-06-18 06:34:10'),
(473, 49, 'D3QW200_Image_forest.jpg', 'Projectors', 'Projectors that display every detail, even in bright daylight. Panasonic has given event\r\nproducers the freedom to create spectacular live shows and 3D mapping events.', 1, 0, 'Right', '2024-06-18 06:34:10', '2024-06-18 06:34:10'),
(474, 49, 'Banner 37 (410x220) - LED Screen, Panasonic for Entertainment.jpg', 'LED Video Wall', 'The LED Video Wall series offers expandability with additional panels, enabling the creation\r\nof a vast and immersive display. Ideal for captivating experiences and beyond.', 1, 0, 'Left', '2024-06-18 06:34:10', '2024-06-18 06:34:10'),
(475, 49, 'Banner 38 (410x220) -  Display, Panasonic for Entertainment.jpg', 'Professional Displays', 'Digital signage, touch screens, video walls and projection mapping. There’s more to\r\nPanasonic Connect than meets the eye.', 1, 0, 'Right', '2024-06-18 06:34:10', '2024-06-18 06:34:10'),
(476, 50, 'Banner 39 - LED Screen, Panasonic for Hospital_.jpg', 'Interactive Displays', 'Hospital-grade televisions must meet more stringent requirements for use in patient rooms,\r\nwaiting rooms,', 1, 0, 'Left', '2024-06-18 06:34:54', '2024-06-18 06:34:54'),
(477, 50, 'Banner 35 (410x220) -  Signage, Panasonic for Restaurant.jpg', 'CMS solutions', 'Panasonic offers powerful software that makes the entire paper-to-digital workflow faster,\r\nsimpler and far more accurate, while protecting sensitive hospital and patient data.', 1, 0, 'Right', '2024-06-18 06:34:54', '2024-06-18 06:34:54'),
(478, 50, 'panasonic-AW-UE150-IBC2018.jpg', 'Broadcast &  ProAV', 'PTZ cameras and remote systems, including auto- and audio-tracking software, to capture\r\ncontent.', 1, 0, 'Left', '2024-06-18 06:34:54', '2024-06-18 06:34:54'),
(479, 51, 'Banner 24 (410x220) - E-Card Signages.jpg', 'eSignCard', 'Businesses can utilize eSignCards to display schedules, speaker profiles, and sponsor information during\r\nconferences. Their clean, purposeful, and minimalist design make them ideal for placement in Boardrooms,\r\nConference Halls, and Top Management Cabins.', 1, 0, 'Left', '2024-06-18 06:35:32', '2024-06-18 06:35:32'),
(480, 51, 'RB_6_Pro_PoE_no-cables_booked.png', 'RoomBook+', 'RoomBook+ is the simplest solution for managing meeting rooms, optimizing board room use, and displaying relevant\r\ninformation where it is needed the most. Built on years of customer feedback, RoomBook+ is designed to upgrade the\r\nmeeting culture and introduce meeting space room management to the modern-day workplace.', 1, 0, 'Right', '2024-06-18 06:35:32', '2024-06-18 06:35:32'),
(481, 51, '1716202139664b2a9b7c1cc.jpg', 'Broadcast & ProAV', 'From those who protect and serve to those who lead; our remotely controlled PTZ cameras\r\ncan be used to share courtroom sessions and government debate in parliaments.', 1, 0, 'Left', '2024-06-18 06:35:32', '2024-06-18 06:35:32'),
(482, 51, 'D3QW200_Image_cave.jpg', 'Projector', 'Training simulations, meeting room projection – whatever you need reliable, high-definition\r\nvisual systems for, we have the hardware and the support.', 1, 0, 'Right', '2024-06-18 06:35:32', '2024-06-18 06:35:32'),
(483, 51, 'lfv9_Airport__rs_low-res.jpg', 'Professional Displays', 'Digital signage, control room surveillance – whatever you need reliable, high-definition\r\nvisual systems for, we have the hardware and the support,', 1, 0, 'Left', '2024-06-18 06:35:32', '2024-06-18 06:35:32'),
(484, 44, 'Banner 22 (410x220) - Professional Display.jpg', 'Professional Display', 'Bring retail and entertainment truly together with our 4K and HD displays, world-class\r\nprojectors, or LED video walls – and create retailtainment like never before.', 1, 0, 'Left', '2024-06-21 11:13:44', '2024-06-21 11:13:44'),
(485, 44, 'Banner 23 (410x220) - Floor Stab.jpg', 'Floor Stand Kiosk', 'There are a range of floor standing digital standees available in both standard and Slim\r\ndesign. Standard design offers both touch and non-touch screen options. Advertising display,\r\ninteractive information release and other functions in indoor environments.', 1, 0, 'Right', '2024-06-21 11:13:45', '2024-06-21 11:13:45'),
(486, 44, 'electronicshelflabels-benefitsforyourcustomers.jpg', 'Electronic Shelf Labels', 'Centralised, efficient price management also known as digital price tags - are digital display\r\nsystems used in retail stores to replace traditional paper price tags or labels on shelves. These\r\nlabels can show information to shoppers such as product pricing, nutrition information,\r\npromotions and stock levels.', 1, 0, 'Left', '2024-06-21 11:13:45', '2024-06-21 11:13:45'),
(487, 44, 'Banner 24 (410x220) - E-Card Signages.jpg', 'eSignCards', 'eSignCards replace paper tent cards within retail stores. They can be strategically placed to\r\nhighlight ongoing promotions, discounts, or loyalty programs. Versatile displays that can\r\nbe used for a wide range of purposes. Centralized management allows retailers to change\r\nprices, update promotions, and synchronize information across multiple locations in\r\nreal-time. At the same time, for small stores, the decentralized approach enables owners /\r\nmanagers to digitally update the eSignCard information across their store using their\r\nmobile phones.', 1, 0, 'Right', '2024-06-21 11:13:45', '2024-06-21 11:13:45');
